												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "Unsure but appreciative, Arc: Halsin spent the past few months building a new community for people left dispossessed by the upheaval the Absolute called. The player did not go with him however, and now they are reuniting at a celebration. This may be purely platonic, or as old flames "
