												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "Betraying a little concern, like a parent's first night out away from the new baby. ,Arc: Halsin spent the past few months building a new community for people left dispossessed by the upheaval the Absolute called. The player is in a relationship with him and has been staying with him at his new community. They arrived at the celebration together."
